Description: R Package for Evaluation Platform in COPD (EPIC). EPIC is a Discrete Event Simulation (DES) model that simulates health outcomes of COPD patients based on demographics and individual-level risk factors. DISCLAIMER: The package is currently under development and should not be used for research and/or clinical applications.
